# Trivy ignore file — accepted (bypassed) vulnerabilities for the app image.
#
# WHY BYPASSED: every finding is fixable ONLY via a MAJOR dependency upgrade that
# breaks the app — langchain 0.2.x -> 0.3/1.x (breaking API migration + the pinned
# langchain-huggingface/langchain-openai), transformers 4 -> 5 (breaks
# sentence-transformers 3.0.1), pillow 10 -> 12 (transitive, streamlit conflicts).
# None are reachable in this app's usage: it does not deserialize untrusted data,
# does not process user-supplied images, and does not set trust_remote_code.
#
# The gate stays FAIL-CLOSED for any *new* fixable HIGH/CRITICAL not listed here.
# TODO: clear these during a dependency-modernization pass (upgrade LangChain stack).

